!! Pills parameters

|!Parameter |!Default |!Description |
|`elements` |`""` |Space-separated list or TW filter |
|`selection` |`"multi"` |`"multi"` or `"single"` |
|`filterable` |`"no"` |`"no"`, `"yes"` (popup), or `"inline"` (search input above pills) |
|`sync-tiddler` |`""` |External tiddler to sync state to |
|`sync-field` |`"text"` |Field on sync-tiddler |
|`state` |auto-generated |State tiddler for selection |
|`instid` |auto-generated |Instance ID for CSS scoping |

!! Pills slots

|!Slot name |!Variables |!Description |
|`view` |`element` |Custom element rendering |
|`on-select` |`element`, `modifier` |Callback on selection change |

!! Vtabs parameters

|!Parameter |!Default |!Description |
|`elements` |`""` |TW filter returning element titles |
|`type-fn` |`""` |Filter to get element type code |
|`state` |auto-generated |State tiddler for active tab |
|`instid` |auto-generated |Instance ID |
|`visible-types` |`"sec"` |Space-separated always-visible type codes |
|`default-collapsed` |`"yes"` |Start with sections collapsed |
|`lnk-navigate` |`"yes"` |Navigate on link-type click |

!! Vtabs slots

|!Slot name |!Variables |!Description |
|`view-sec` |`element` |Render for type `sec` |
|`view-act` |`element` |Render for type `act` |
|`view-pop` |`element` |Render for type `pop` (popup) |
|`view-lnk` |`element` |Render for type `lnk` (link) |
|`view-sco` |`element` |Render for type `sco` (scope) |
|`view-spa` |`element` |Render for type `spa` (spacer) |
|`view` |`element` |Fallback render for unknown types |

!! Mixin functions — Layer 0 (rrc0.*)

|!Function |!Purpose |
|`rrc0.elems()` |Returns element list (space-separated or filter) |
|`rrc0.elem-type(element)` |Maps element to type code |
|`rrc0.elem-visible(element)` |Visibility filter for element |
|`rrc0.elem-view(element)` |Rendering dispatch |
|`rrc0.elem-clicked(element)` |Click handler dispatch |
|`rrc0.elem-add-class(element)` |CSS class dispatch |

!! Mixin functions — Layer 1 (rrc1.*)

|!Function |!Purpose |
|`rrc1.elem-clicked:<type>(element)` |Type-specific click handler |
|`rrc1.elem-view:<type>(element)` |Type-specific view |
|`rrc1.state.tiddler(key, uid)` |Returns state tiddler title |
|`rrc1.state.prefix()` |Returns state tiddler prefix |
|`rrc1.state.field(key)` |Returns state field name |
|`rrc1.elem-selected(tiddler, field, element, yes, no)` |Check if element is selected |
|`rrc1.elem-add-class(element)` |Returns CSS class for selected state |

!! CSS classes

|!Class |!Description |
|`.rrc-component` |Inner component container |
|`.rrc-elem` |Individual element (click target) |
|`.selected` |Added to selected elements |
|`.rrc-type-<code>` |Per-type styling hook (e.g., `.rrc-type-sec`) |
|`.rrc-pills` |Pills container scope |
|`.rrc-vtabs` |Vtabs container scope |
|`.rrc-pills-inline-filter` |Inline filter input container |
|`.rrc-no-propagate` |Stops click propagation — wrap interactive elements in vtabs fills with this class to prevent row click handlers from firing |

</$fill>
</$transclude>
